ABSTRACT
A multilayer electronic component includes a first multilayer
capacitor electrically connected to a first surface of a support
plate formed of an insulating material; and first and second
metal frames electrically connected to first and second ends
of the support plate, respectively. The first and second metal
frames extend in an amount greater than a thickness of the
first multilayer capacitor so that a first end of the first and
second metal frames constitutes a mounting part.
